{"id": "1467225902029996154", "channel_id": "1467225902029996154", "type": 0, "author_id": "1060975277531992145", "author_name": "arandomflamev2", "author_bot": false, "content": "This is about the description of the devour effect on leigh and if it works as intended.\nBy description the devour effect on leigh restores 16% of lost hp and doubles the STR gained from her exalt. \nThe description of Scion of Purity, is that when devoured it triggers the devour effect twice. If Leigh's exalt triggers a devour with a scion, while it restores hp two times as intended, its str gain is a bit weird.\nOn a normal devour Leigh gains 2x str.\nOn a devour with Scion of Purity Leigh gains 3x str. By how the description of the effects work, shouldn't the str gained be doubled 2 times, aka quadrupled?\nI attached a video showcasing all the str gains of leigh depending on type of devour and exalt and overexalt.", "timestamp": "2026-01-31T18:31:54.783000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-01T14:56:04.002000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1467225906207789156", "filename": "leigh_str.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 83948339, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1467225902029996154/1467225906207789156/leigh_str.mp4?ex=69fb891b&is=69fa379b&hm=1cb5f93f0a075168e1ccff0f47012b9f9031bee128964f4f86306b8f9ed8f7df&"}, {"id": "1467225910695563498", "filename": "exal.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 55534, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1467225902029996154/1467225910695563498/exal.png?ex=69fb891c&is=69fa379c&hm=5211115ad7de01c148a9938323d1d05d40c203025ed9b699268c9e94529fac65&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1467225902029996154", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Leigh STR gain possible bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168939622727801", "1361168893200044183"]}
